comment: Amber Heard  is a liar. She lied the whole trial. She must to be punished.
commentable_entity.title: Charge Amber Heard with Perjury
commentable_entity.description:
Amber Heard has lied on the stand in court. There are consequences set in place to protect the integrity of our legal system. This integrity must be upheld. 

Amber Heard and her legal team are continuing to lie even after the verdict. They have accused the Judge and Jury of impropriety. This is unacceptable. 

She must be held accountable for her actions and words. 

Sign this petition if you agree that Amber Heard should be charged with Perjury for the lies she told on the stand.
